rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0001
rows.name:
Awww, yay!
So awesome. Woooo!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0002
rows.name:
Just lookit!
I'm literally speechless!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0003
rows.name:
I never saw a view like this before.
Not in my whole life!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0004
rows.name:
It gladdens me to see you so enthused.
The view is breath-taking indeed.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0005
rows.name:
I can't remember you getting so excited
about scenery, Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0006
rows.name:
But you've seen a whole bunch of stuff
like this...

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0007
rows.name:
Really, Ibuki? But you've seen all kinds
of vistas, without reacting like this.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0008
rows.name:
C'mon, you've seen all this wind and
water crap before. What's the big deal
this time?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0009
rows.name:
Huh?
Really...?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0010
rows.name:
Uh... Maybe...?
But this one's just so crazy-awesome!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0011
rows.name:
Are you sure you're not
misremembering?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0012
rows.name:
Ah, that's the cool thing about all this
adventuring business. Coming across
stuff like this!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0013
rows.name:
I just wanna keep doing it. I just wanna
see everything, discover it all!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0014
rows.name: Hey, Ibuki...

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0015
rows.name: So what is it you want to see next?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0016
rows.name: You really like adventures, don't you?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0017
rows.name: Hey, Ibuki...

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0018
rows.name: Where'd you wanna to go next?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0019
rows.name: You really like adventures, huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0020
rows.name: Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0021
rows.name: What would you like to see next?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0022
rows.name:
You have a penchant for adventures,
I see.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0023
rows.name: So, Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0024
rows.name: Where'd you want to go next?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0025
rows.name:
You've got a wacky craving for
adventures, don't ya?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0101
rows.name: Hmmm.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0102
rows.name: I really want to see somewhere snowy.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0103
rows.name: Snowy, you say...

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0104
rows.name:
Yup!
I've never seen snow in real life before.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0105
rows.name:
Ah, I can just imagine it. Everything all
white, like a great big wedding cake.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0106
rows.name:
But... Didn't we see rather a lot of snow
in Luxuria? We were only just there...

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0107
rows.name: Uh? Dondle...? It had snow? Seriously?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0108
rows.name:
Oh... Wait, wait...don't tell me...
Umm...

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0109
rows.name:
Did like, all you guys go on the sly, and
leave out ol' Ibuki here?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0110
rows.name: That was pretty lame of you jerks!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0111
rows.name:
Hey! We haven't kept anything from
you, Ibuki. Byakko, are you sure
we saw some snow...?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0112
rows.name:
Hey, calm down, will you? Are you sure
flea-bag here didn't just remember it
wrong?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0113
rows.name:
Ibuki, we never leave a man behind.
Could Byakko be mistaken?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0114
rows.name:
Ibuki, we wouldn't do the dirty on you
without a really good reason. Maybe
Byakko just got it wrong.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0115
rows.name:
Huh? Ah, well perhaps I am mistaken.
Think of it that way, if it makes you feel
better.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0116
rows.name:
Bah, you guys!
I knew you wouldn't have stabbed me
in the back like that.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0117
rows.name:
And for the record, if you're going off
somewhere, don't forget to tell 
ol' Ibuki about it!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0118
rows.name:
And y'know another place I wanna
see? A real hot place, with scorched
earth! A fusty ol' dust bowl!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0119
rows.name:
I feel like I'd really be able to spread
my wings and fly in a place like that.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0120
rows.name: Really... I'm not so sure.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0121
rows.name:
Huh, whatever! Just make sure you tell
me if you're about to go off to one of
those crazy-cool places!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0201
rows.name:
Yeah! I really love 'em! It's what makes
all this wandering about worthwhile.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0202
rows.name:
Seeing new stuff... It's what it's all
about!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0203
rows.name:
Hey... I was just saying exactly the
same thing, like, just a minute ago...

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0204
rows.name: ...Right?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0205
rows.name:
Ah who cares. I'm probably just
overthinking it!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0206
rows.name:
Hahaha... Don't worry, Ibuki. We're
used to it, and we love you all the
same.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0207
rows.name:
Huh...? You guys don't seem as
worked up about all this new stuff as
me. Don't you like new things?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0208
rows.name: Nah, I mean, we like them, Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0209
rows.name:
We just don't get quite as excited as
you do!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0210
rows.name:
Nah, I mean, this stuff is still kinda cool,
Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0211
rows.name:
We just don't go nuts and flip a lid
every time.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0212
rows.name:
No, seeing new things builds character,
I can't deny that.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0213
rows.name: But a soldier's got to keep their dignity.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0214
rows.name:
Don't get me wrong, Ibuki, it's good to
see something new.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0215
rows.name:
But some of us have super-cool,
ice-man reps to maintain.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0216
rows.name: Seriously?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0217
rows.name: Indeed, Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0218
rows.name:
You have your own...very loud...way
of rejoicing. It's one of your
characteristics.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0219
rows.name:
Uh... I... I don't...r-really get when you...
Eh, who cares!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0301
rows.name:
But anyhow... Let's hurry on to the
next great discovery! I can't wait!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0302
rows.name: Everyone good to go?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0303
rows.name:
Very much so!
Let us venture forth!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0304
rows.name: Yeah! Woohoo!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0305
rows.name: Look! Lookit!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0306
rows.name:
Get a load of that scenery!
Never seen that before!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0307
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0308
rows.name:
Hey, can't you see that killer view,
Bromarch? It rocks!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0309
rows.name: What... Did you forget already?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0310
rows.name:
Forget?
Forget what?

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0311
rows.name: Hahaha!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0312
rows.name:
Ibuki, I don't think we'll ever get bored
while you're around!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0313
rows.name: Hahaha!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0314
rows.name:
We'll never be short of entertainment
with you around, Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0315
rows.name: Hahaha!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0316
rows.name:
Every platoon needs someone like you,
Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0317
rows.name: Hahaha!

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0318
rows.name: You're an absolute classic, Ibuki.

rows.label: kizunatalk077_msg0319
rows.name:
Wh-What are you talking about?
You're all weird...
